{"tid":621482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果照相機】為言論自由打氣！","createTime":"2018-04-08T10:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T11:13:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"95ea4f02fa90ecdb1438a52c9e8ac8f6ff1eace9","tid":621482,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180408/20355498\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355498&d=Xtjo5GBSm4Pu%2BzG1FjlExE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8f382bce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180408%2F20355498&h=f2074df8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180408/20355498</a><br />\n<br />\n【蘋果照相機】為言論自由打氣！<br />\n<br />\n頭條   <br />\n         <br />\n一張照片勝過千言萬語！<br />\n<br />\n攝影師每日以相機拍下千百萬張照片，將一些大家看似熟悉的東西，以用不同的觀點與角度，讓你重新細看。<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果照相機】為大家呈現新聞重要時刻，以細膩照片，分享鏡頭背後的甜酸苦樂。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果攝記fb： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/1OlyZxX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F1OlyZxX&d=Xtjo5GBSm4Pu%2BzG1FjlExE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=2931844a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/1OlyZxX</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t參加者：危機逼近不能麻木<br />\n頭條 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t譚耀宗抹黑戴組織港獨工作<br />\n頭條 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t港獨派另辦集會　數十人出席<br />\n頭條 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t中大學生會前幹事被拒入境澳門<br />\n頭條 4小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t二千人集會撐戴耀廷李柱銘藉防波堤籲團結「大家蹺埋先有實力」<br />\n頭條 4小時前"},{"pid":"ca915397c78ce51aa503f19fd1c5e0ceaef7506a","tid":621482,"uid":35815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:10:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d1c0ec15b16675b7ff1526ac6126ca6f0c5b3bf","tid":621482,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:13:02.000Z","msg":"泛民唔比學生上台演講喎<img src=\"/asset